泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 惊喜亮相《周六夜现场》(SNL) 赛季首播https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-makes-surprise-appearance-on-snl-season-premiere-3515101?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=taylor-swift-makes-surprise-appearance- SNL 季节首映Alex RigottiSun, 15 Oct 2023 08:24:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopSaturday Night Live https://www.nme.com/?p=3515101 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在新泽西州 2023 年 MTV VMA 红毯上摆出姿势" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位流行歌星与艾斯·斯派斯 (Ice Spice) 一起出现，后者是该集的音乐嘉宾</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-makes-surprise-appearance-on-snl-season-premiere-3515101">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 惊喜亮相《周六夜现场》(SNL) 季首播后，</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上发表。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在新泽西州 2023 年 MTV VMA 红毯上摆出姿势" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TaylorSwift-MTV-VMAs-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swifthttps://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/saturday-night-live">《周六夜现场</a></em>》季首播中出人意料地客串。</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE:<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-concert-movie-3513715">&#39;Taylor Swift: The Eras Tour&#39; concert film review: this is cinema (Taylor&#39;s version)</a></strong></li></ul><p> SNL kicked off its 49th season last night (October 14) with <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pete-davidson">Pete Davidson</a> as its host and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a> on musical duties. The long-running sketch show also revealed <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-bunny">Bad Bunny</a> would <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/saturday-night-live-announces-first-performers-and-guests-for-season-49-3509700">host and perform in an upcoming episode</a> .</p><p> Swift arrived to introduce Ice Spice&#39;s second performance of the night, &#39;Pretty Girl&#39; ft. <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rema">Rema</a> . Normally, the host would introduce the musical guest (as Pete Davison did for the Bronx rapper&#39;s first performance, &#39;In Ha Mood&#39;). However, it seems an exception was made for Ice Spice.</p><p> She and Swift recently worked on the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swifts-self-directed-video-for-karma-featuring-ice-spice-3448830">&#39;Karma&#39;</a> remix, with the singer-songwriter commenting that Ice Spice “impresses the hell out of me”. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Ice Spice: Pretty Girl (Live) - SNL" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/s3FzkxeEACE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> A sketch was also performed earlier in the episode, where a panel of sports commentators (played by Davidson and the SNL cast) tried to discuss a football game without mentioning Swift&#39;s new relationship with NFL player Travis Kelce. Kelce, a footballer for Kansas City Chiefs, made his own surprise appearance towards the end of the sketch.</p><p> He also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-kelce-addresses-interest-in-documentary-since-taylor-swift-dating-rumours-3513709">recently addressed the media frenzy</a> surrounding his relationship with the popstar on his podcast with his brother, Jason. Kelce released his documentary on <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">Amazon Prime Video</a> last month (September 12); it is now the platform&#39;s most-watched documentary in the US.</p><p> “How crazy is that?” asked Jason, and further joked: “All because of you and me, it doesn&#39;t have anything to do with this Taylor Swift drama.”</p><p> Travis continued to make light of the situation, replying: “That&#39;s what I&#39;m saying man, everybody&#39;s just so interested in the family dynamic… I thought that was pretty cool. That&#39;s fun to hang your hat on.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Fox NFL Sunday - SNL" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IUgHMGb74ZM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p> Swift&#39;s appearance on SNL coincides with the opening weekend of &#39;The Eras Tour&#39; film. In our<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-concert-movie-3513715">four-star review</a> , <em>NME</em> said of the film: ” It&#39;s a staggering feat. In the space of one seamless performance, Swift is at turns a playfully eccentric artist, a country star and a genuine pop icon. Yet for all the spectacle, it might be those acoustic songs that linger longest in the memory.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-makes-surprise-appearance-on-snl-season-premiere-3515101">Taylor Swift makes surprise appearance on SNL season premiere</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
